---
title: Cheesy Chorizo Enchiladas with Black Beans and Citrus Salad
description: Mexican food is recognised by UNESCO as an 'Intangible Cultural Heritage of Humanity'… Basically, Mexican food is undeniably delicious! Like this enchilada recipe, which is bursting with black beans and chorizo. ¡Buen provecho!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheesy-chorizo-enchiladas-f6481d85-d39d13ae.jpg
